text: Per-Olof Claesson (born 23 January 1965) is a Swedish rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
